						<summary>

						<p>Fragment of a slab in the field of Santayyagāri Sangayya.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to refer to a gift (details lost) made to Ṇarāsījiyya, probably by Biṭṭayarasa and seems to refer to the latter's camp at Sindinīra.</p>						

						<p>This borken and incomplete record is in characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
